column2: Leap toward your destination, damaging foes upon impact.

Use to construct a superior shield generator build site. The generator's primary function is to project force fields in order to disrupt enemy movement and support allies. Range 3,300. Requires 50 supply to complete.
<c=@abilitytype>Elixir.</c> Shoot an elixir orb, healing nearby allies when it bursts and creating an area of continual healing.
This feature requires upgrading to Guild Wars 2: Heart of Thorns. To upgrade your account, purchase Guild Wars 2: Path of Fire and get Guild Wars 2: Heart of Thorns for FREE.
